Instructions to run sample app

{-- Need to be on a corporate network --}

1. Install GPM instruction is on:
https://intranet.genesys.com/display/CUFG/Genesys+Package+Manager

2. Use GPM to install lib under app:
gpm install

2.1 install git if needed 

2.2 If bower_component does not install because git not is allowed in firewall:
git config --global url."https://".insteadOf git://

{-- Need to be on a public network --}

3. Run the following command to install all the dependencies:
npm install

4. Run the following command to build and start running test:
grunt

4.1 to run server
grunt serve
